description:
Applicability
This schedule is applicable and restricted to pumping of ground water for drainage or irrigation for the purpose of Agricultural/Livestock Production within the irrigation service area boundary where such pumping is eligible to be served with electricity sold to the District by the City and County of San Francisco pursuant to Section 9(l) of the federal Raker Act. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
Connected Load Charge, per HP:
Winter Billing Months $ 1.56
Summer Billing Months $ 2.26
name: Schedule PT Restricted Irrigation Pumping Time-Of-Use
